            <div type="translation" ana="b1 b2">
                <p>... In faith like Abraham; in friendship like Isaac; in hope like Jacob; in
                    humility like Moses; in glory like David; in wisdom like Solomon; in endurance
                    like Job.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Figueras suggested φιλίαν may be the virtue attributed to Isaac; Negev hesitated
                    to suggest any reconstruction.</p>
            </div>
